item.description: ALBERTTT Team RRQ Alberttt × Youtube facebook Facebook photo_camera Instagram flutter_dash Twitter sports_esports ALBERTTT sports_esports Team RRQ Close More Info Alberttt Bio Introduction Sejak kecil, Albert Nielsen Iskandar memang hobi bermain gim.
